channel.description:
alright, yo. I got this cache downloader. and it *almost* works. right? but... well look.
[img]http://img854.imageshack.us/img854/1926/erroryi.png[/img]
the one on the right is within the DC folder on the left. the entire left side isn't necessary, its supposed to go directly from C: -> DC -> to the one on the right... if you understand what im saying...
